                .ml-3
                  p.text-sm.text-yellow-700
                    strong Note: 
                    | Technically some have three states as don't forget the physical buttons on the board - these will activate the functionality AND have 
                    = link_to "secret functionality", "/boards/baldrick17/board_buttons", class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline"

